      <h1>Promote Seasonal Campaigns with Video Production</h1>
      <p class="lead">Discover how video production helps brands promote seasonal campaigns, with formats and channels that drive engagement and sales.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>November 21, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 24, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
